{"tid":1933930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎》台灣實力展現 歐盟也宣布與中研院合作開發疫苗和快篩","createTime":"2020-03-19T15:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T10:29:53.000Z","uid":141151,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"979ab7f5da805ba07df6b4552a1836b61adb798c","tid":1933930,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:00:31.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎》台灣實力展現 歐盟也宣布與中研院合作開發疫苗和快篩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3104643\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3104643&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFY26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=469b1b6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3104643&h=f09321d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3104643</a><br />\n<br />\n〔記者簡惠茹／台北報導〕台灣研究實力陸續吸引各國尋求合作，繼外交部與美國在台協會（AIT）今天同步發表「臺美防疫夥伴關係聯合聲明」，歐盟駐台代表也宣布，歐盟和台灣合作開發快篩和疫苗，有信心可以擊敗冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲經貿辦事處處長高哲夫（Filip Grzegorzewski）今天在Twitter上宣布，歐盟和台灣中研院同心協力合作開發快篩和疫苗，有了15分鐘就能得到可靠結果的測試，相信我們可以擊敗冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n而針對台美合作聲明，外交部說明，6大合作抗疫措施包括快篩檢驗試劑的研發、疫苗的研究與生產、藥品的研究與生產、追蹤接觸者相關技術機制與科技、舉行科學家與專家的聯合會議及防疫醫療用品及設備的合作與交流。<br />\n<br />\n中研院今晚表示，為使研究能量最大化，台灣積極與國外接洽合作，裡應外合，攜手抗疫，昨天美國在台協會（AIT）處長酈英傑與中研院長廖俊智會面，討論台美對抗新冠肺炎策略，雙方將進一步強化公衛與防疫合作機制。<br />\n<br />\n中研院表示，中研院已於2月聯合國內學研單位，組成擁有13個子平台的抗疫平台，從篩檢、藥物、疫苗等不同面向著手研發，採分進合擊方式，前幾周在藥物合成和快篩試劑上都有突破性的進展。"},{"pid":"5abcebc53a0520a53b30597533fed693c6c23f98","tid":1933930,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d169c74b6c1fae71b0348aed7c0af8aefb88b14d","tid":1933930,"uid":5103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:02:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">[本土youtube戰線][黃頁］面對偷圖狗，我哋創作愈做愈灰心（認真post)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932944\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1932944</a><br />\n<br />\n我地已經比人抄到灰哂機<br />\n想請巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ce7268ed7023b2c9767409ca78852da86efaea","tid":1933930,"uid":169074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:04:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1b4bc02afcee058aef3ce23239f64536791dd50","tid":1933930,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/BeneficialAnxiousHellbender-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FBeneficialAnxiousHellbender-size_restricted.gif&h=15a7afc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a5a926cc770b915ea9d971fdd2ef92c16960e16","tid":1933930,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:08:12.000Z","msg":"真正大國"},{"pid":"97a52012d37a136faa7663bb545b0f6c82708fd0","tid":1933930,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:10:09.000Z","msg":"Taiwan No.1"},{"pid":"39c0ae2043dc6f9b1a4d4826e9417b663e47a6aa","tid":1933930,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"WHO?who fucking cares"},{"pid":"2b747bf870b999d278a201a50b7757ffbe2bd6c3","tid":1933930,"uid":56819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:13:37.000Z","msg":"好心就解散世衛啦,玩到爛晒臭晒,全世界加埋台灣重新設立一個新嘅組織,唔好再侵支那玩"},{"pid":"83be44de948b93e7e6f384f9c3cda2d6dd184dbd","tid":1933930,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:14:08.000Z","msg":"口交部提出嚴重抗議<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7cb22bff8e725a861f6e127cda2295dab995f5","t